title: $1,000/month One Bdrm Apt:  Bi-level-Main Floor
posting_body: ['APARTMENT FOR RENT:    Bi-level-Main Floor:  $1,000/month.', ' Very Clean, Large One Bedroom + One Bathroom + Laundry Room (hook-ups) in your unit.', ' No Pets, Smoke Free Unit.', ' Includes:   Central Air Conditioning, Washer and Dryer hook-ups.', 'Stove, Refrigerator.', ' Senior Discount Available.', 'REQUIREMENTS:  Minimum 2 Year Lease Agreement.', '  Good Credit Required - Application Form, Background Check, Credit Report and Income and Length of Employment Verification.', 'REQUIREMENTS: ($3,500 Required Upfront to Move-in.)', " This Consists of First Month's Rent $1,000 plus Last Month's Rent $1,000 plus $1,000 Security Deposit plus $500 Prepaid Cleaning.", ' All Utilities are paid by Tenant.', 'By Appointment Only.', 'Call number listed in this Ad or Respond to this Ad,', 'Thank you.']
